---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<main>
		<a href="home" class="flex flex-col items-center bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 via-pink-500 to-blue-500 border2 border-purple-600 rounded-lg shadow-md md:flex-row md:max-w-4xl mx-auto hover:from-purple-600 hover:via-pink-600 hover:to-blue-600 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 pl-8 pr-5">
			<img class="object-cover w-60 rounded-t-lg h-96  md:rounded-none md:rounded-l-lg neon-glow pr-2" src="./assets/photo.jpg" alt="">
			<div class="flex flex-col justify-between p-4 leading-normal">
				<h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-200 dark:text-white neon-text">Noktho Solaire</h5>
				<p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 neon-text text-justify">Step into the cosmic realm of web development where creativity and innovation know no limits. Welcome to my stellar portfolio, where I blend the wonders of space with cutting-edge technology. Like a rocket soaring through the digital universe, I craft captivating websites that transport users to otherworldly experiences. With every line of code, I weave the intricate tapestry of celestial aesthetics and seamless functionality. From mesmerizing parallax scrolling to sleek intergalactic interfaces, my designs defy gravity and push the boundaries of user experience. Whether you seek a stellar e-commerce platform or a celestial showcase for your brand, I bring your vision to life in the vastness of cyberspace. Embark on this cosmic journey, where the stars align with responsive layouts, stellar animations, and pixel-perfect designs. Join me as we explore the interstellar possibilities of the web, where imagination meets innovation and the universe becomes our canvas. Together, let's boldly go where no website has gone before.</p>
				<button type="button" class="text-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900 via-pink-900 to-blue-900 border border-purple-800 focus:outline-none hover:from-purple-800 hover:via-pink-800 hover:to-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-purple-500 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 mr-2 mb-2 neon-text dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 dark:focus:ring-gray-700">Let's begin our journey</button>
			</div>
		</a>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
	align-items: center;
	flex-direction: column;
	height: 100vh;
	margin: auto;
	padding: 1.5rem;
	max-width: 600ch;
	/* backdrop-filter: blur(8px); */
	opacity: 0.96;
	}
	

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		/* background-image: url('./assets/background.png'); */
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.instructions {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
		background-color: white;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.4rem;
	}
	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.875em;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 12%);
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.3em 0.45em;
	}
	.instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
